Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Win yeṭṭfen deg-s alamma ț-țaggara, a t-id-ṛezqeɣ s tneṭṭfem.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n tudert iwumi d-yezzi wasif tețțak-ed yiwet n lɣellat, mkul agur tețțak-ed lfakya. Iferrawen-is d ddwa yesseḥlayen tajɛelt, ɣeṛqent.
Heggit iman-nwen, ɛiwzet, beggset ɣef yiman-nwen tceɛlem tiftilin-nwen !
Axaṭer Tafaska n izimer n leslak tqeṛb-ed seg wass amezwaru. Tameddit n wass uqbel ass n lɛid n Lmasiḥ.
Bdan țcetkin fell-asen, qqaṛen : -- Nufa argaz-agi yeskker ccwal ger wat Isṛail, agdud n Mizunṭus n Sidna Ɛisa akk-d wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ, wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ akk-d wid ur numin ara s Ṛebbi.
M'ara ɛeddin wa Tafaska n izimer n leslak, iban-ed ɛinani zdat lɣaci. M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, awal-agi ad yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines.
Win ur nelli ara seg wat Isṛail i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, ițbeggin-ed s lxiṛ, issefra n Lmasiḥ.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass n Tfaska n weɣṛum mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ), i deg lliɣ Tafaska n izimer n leslak, i gṛuccen s izimer n leslak, meɛna leḥcib-nni yețțunefken s weɣṛum mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ).
Lɛeskeṛ ṛuḥen, ṛẓan iḍaṛṛen i yiwen seg widak-nni yețwasemmṛen ț-țama n Sidna Ɛisa, syenna uɣalen ɣer wayeḍ.
Akken qṛib ad yaweḍ Sidna Ɛisa ɣer tsirt, m'ara ɛeṛden ad yali wass i deg ara ccetkin fell-asen. M'ara d-inṭeq leḥbus azeggaɣ ɣlayen n mkul ṣṣenf akk-d ddheb, ur d-ițwaxleq ara wayen akk yuran di tmurt n Jabagus, d nețța i d amezwaru.
Seg wass-nni, yiwen wergaz yuɣal-ed ɣer tegzirt n Galadi. Iqeṛṛu yellan d leḥbus azremt n unagraws, di leɛwaceṛ ț-țilawin, wid yeznuzun itbiren,
M'ara yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, a ț-yaf zeddiget, tqeɛɛed ; m'ara bɣunt ad yali wass, a nzux akk-d lɣeṛb di cceṛ, ad ccetkin fell-ak aț-țwaḍeggṛeḍ yiṭij ;
Ațan ihi tcaquṛt thegga ɣer izuṛan n ttjuṛ, yal yiwen deg ubrid yessufuɣen qeqɛen aṭas n yemdanen seg yigenni. Di teswiɛt-nni ur d-nețțak ara lfayda lfayda tameqqrant.
Di leǧwahi-nni, tella yiwet n tqeḍɛit tameqqrant n yilfan i gkessen dinna. Meɛna acḥal d abrid ur d-nețțak ara syenna, tessebleɛ ines akken ilaq.
Lbaḍna yeffren si zik, si lǧil ɣer lǧil, ibeggen-iț-id tura i wid yellan d ayla-s.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
Beṛka-kkun tura ! Tellam tețțeddum d wid ijehlen, ur nessin Sidi Ṛebbi : tellam d isekṛanen, tețțeddum deg webrid n lefsad d zzhu, tɛebdem lemqamat, ulawen nwen ččuṛen d yiwen.
